title: Russell Wilson, Jarrett Stidham, Dana White, Tua Tagovailoa
itunes:title: Russell Wilson, Jarrett Stidham, Dana White, Tua Tagovailoa
description:
Colin talks about another example of Russell Wilson being disrespected, why he feels Jarrett Stidham isn't special, why he's defending Dana White, and why Tua Tagovailoa is going to be a star in the NFL. Guests include Peter King, Joel Klatt, Sam Monson, and Les Snead.
